AMENDEDANALYSIS
Thisbill:
I. Permits schools to hire an owner's project manager (OPM) before entering into a contract for
designservicesinorderforanOPMtorepresentaschoolthroughoutthedesignprocess.
II. Requires that a hired OPM maintain no contractual conflicts of interest with any architect,
design team member, or general contractor hired by a school for a construction or
reconstruction/renovationproject.
III. Increases the threshold cost for projects where a school district or chartered public school is
requiredtohireanOPM.
